docs {
  **Purpose:** Permanently deletes an evaluation request.

  **Auth:** Session cookie (`readi_auth_token`). Requires `view_planning_advanced` permission.

  **Used in:**
  - Planning Dashboard — delete confirmation on evaluation items
}